text: Pushpalatha Jagannath is an Indian politician and the 21st mayor of Mysore between 2019-2020 and a former Deputy Mayor. == Career == Jagannath is an Indian National Congress politician. In November 2018. In 2010 she became a Deputy Mayor of Mysore. She became the 21st Mayor of Mysore. She contested from the ward no 11 at Mysore, where she contested for the second time. == References == Category:Living people Category:Indian National Congress politicians from Karnataka Category:Politicians from Mysore Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
